data.description: Seller has found their next home, make this one yours! Beautifully upgraded 3 bed 2 bath home in Wheeler Ranch! This home features a spacious great room with the kitchen overlooking the space. Beautiful natural light in the main living area. The kitchen features light granite counters with lots of counter and cabinet space plus a dining bar. The flooring throughout the house is all matching laminate. The 3 bedrooms are all down the hallway. The bathrooms have been beautifully remodeled for a spa-like feel. There is a large landscaped backyard with a covered patio. There is more than enough room to entertain or add a pool. The laundry room is on the way into the garage and it features cabinets. This home has a 2 car garage. The pride in ownership shows in this home! Check out the 3D tour!
